Promiscuous mode might be security risk?
-> Change infrastructure to use bridged networking?

Debian 12 uses systemd-networkd
-> /etc/network/interfaces is not used at all
-> either remove systemd-networkd OR set up systemd.service 
	to make eth0 promiscuous at boot
	-> guide https://alias454.com/using-a-systemd-service-file-to-control-promiscuous-mode-automatically-at-boot/